Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for cases involving Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Average time between Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time it takes from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time until Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time for Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to lead to a successful Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for cases rejected by PRE_APPROVER before being approved by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time for Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER in cases that were previously rejected by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER leading to Payment Handled without rejections
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER to the next activity in the process flow
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case
